545
00:52:08,126 --> 00:52:11,927
Well, I'm... I'm just kinda hungry.

546
00:52:17,602 --> 00:52:19,001
Wait. Where we going?

547
00:52:19,004 --> 00:52:21,403
You wanna get something to eat,
we can get something to eat.

