583
00:54:20,724 --> 00:54:21,925
I don't know.

584
00:54:22,827 --> 00:54:24,094
You don't know?

585
00:54:25,096 --> 00:54:26,829
Go on, get something to eat.

586
00:54:27,231 --> 00:54:29,864
