647
00:58:34,112 --> 00:58:36,573
Just that... there ain't much hope for the dead.

648
00:58:39,516 --> 00:58:40,850
Where's your hope?

649
00:58:40,852 --> 00:58:42,085
I have hope.

650
00:58:42,987 --> 00:58:44,653
I have hope for my sister.

651
00:58:44,855 --> 00:58:49,458
You know, and that-and
that... she can be happy.

652
00:58:49,460 --> 00:58:51,193
