653
00:58:53,796 --> 00:58:57,466
Well, what's his name ain't
gonna get that chance, is he?

654
00:58:57,468 --> 00:58:59,967
- Teddy?
- Yeah.

655
00:59:00,070 --> 00:59:01,569
No, he ain't.

656
00:59:12,115 --> 00:59:14,415
- What you watching?
- Sitcom.

657
00:59:16,786 --> 00:59:19,887
- Knew he was gonna say that.
- Why'd you laugh, then?

658
00:59:20,124 --> 00:59:21,564
'Cause it's funny.

659
00:59:27,831 --> 00:59:31,067
So, I guess you think you're pretty funny, then.

660
00:59:31,469 --> 00:59:34,969
- Funnier than you.
- Oh, yeah?

661
00:59:36,140 --> 00:59:37,200
Yeah.

662
00:59:47,017 --> 00:59:48,951
Don't get my hair wet.

663
00:59:49,153 --> 00:59:50,313
Sorry.

664
01:00:08,505 --> 01:00:11,405
