01:01:12,770 --> 01:01:14,537
If that's alright?

672
01:01:15,639 --> 01:01:17,239
Yeah, it's fine.

673
01:01:17,241 --> 01:01:19,207
Just don't push it, OK? We're going to sleep.

674
01:01:20,611 --> 01:01:21,751
Alright.

675
01:01:33,589 --> 01:01:36,924
Don't forget, we got dinner tomorrow
night with Gordon and my mom.

676
01:01:36,927 --> 01:01:37,987
Yeah.

677
01:02:26,043 --> 01:02:28,475
- We're here.
- Yep.

678
01:02:29,546 --> 01:02:32,048
