684
01:03:07,551 --> 01:03:10,185
Um... do you think you want to park here, though?

685
01:03:10,187 --> 01:03:12,287
'Cause my... my neighbors, they
might see something, or...

686
01:03:12,289 --> 01:03:15,022
Well, you'd better hurry up
and go get it, then. Go on.

687
01:03:23,900 --> 01:03:26,300
Well, look who's back from his big im...

688
01:03:45,490 --> 01:03:48,689
- Hey! Who's your friend?
- Mind your own business.

689
01:03:57,600 --> 01:03:58,934
OK.

690
01:03:58,936 --> 01:04:00,936
You can get your car at the train station.

691
01:04:01,038 --> 01:04:02,905
