694
01:04:08,846 --> 01:04:10,145
I gave you the money. It's in there.

695
01:04:10,147 --> 01:04:13,315
Address?

696
01:04:13,317 --> 01:04:14,449
Right.

697
01:04:14,451 --> 01:04:18,719
