727
01:07:50,634 --> 01:07:51,833
Come in.

728
01:07:57,974 --> 01:08:00,841
You watch yourself. Alright?

729
01:08:01,344 --> 01:08:02,743
Yes, ma'am.

730
01:08:09,587 --> 01:08:13,855
Hey. What's this I hear about
